Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.66,0:00:20.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在坠入
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.37,0:00:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沉睡之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.34,0:00:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每当遭遇悲伤与不安之时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.23,0:00:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我便会坠入
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从痛苦的事情中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.79,0:00:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要睁开眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家就能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.96,0:00:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介是为了什么才不断重复永远的第一学期
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.54,0:00:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了让软弱的我变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.35,0:00:53.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介可是赌上了一切奋战到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超越我吧  理树
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.92,0:00:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.36,0:01:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须克服自己的软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.42,0:01:12.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去寻找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.88,0:01:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成这样  是什么时候开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.73,0:01:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后去克服它
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.53,0:01:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候的我有心理创伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.78,0:01:40.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要更远一些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.93,0:02:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:38.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  是从这里开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了逃避悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.42,0:02:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我坠入了沉睡之中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…并不想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要活着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会有所失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还尚未出生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不知道世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但却知道今后会有所失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要活着就会有所失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此  不出生不是也挺好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌悲伤的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想永远待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里的  是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想与你们相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明迟早会失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是想与你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然相遇了就有一天会失去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去很可怕也很悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  比起失去的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相遇的喜悦更为强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:57.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想见到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想见到大家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,许多无可替代的时光在等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诞生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向着新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:48.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要在这里活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和铃  和大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去救大家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:06:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我也会努力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:07:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会再把自己封闭起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后要向大家说出之前无法说出口的谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要尽情欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:10.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和小毬  恭介  谦吾  真人他们一起欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去救大家  和理树一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们做自己力所能及的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦引燃后果将不堪设想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前要将大家一个个搬到外面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没有意识  但脉搏还很清晰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧时间  铃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先把大家从巴士里抬出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再搬到远一点的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬  稍微等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介在堵着车底的洞  不让燃料漏出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠着自己  保护了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:12.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快救恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.94,0:09:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是现在搬动恭介  燃料就会流出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会白费了恭介保护大家的好意了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:26.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介不希望如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先搬大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:33.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:35.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会回来的  等我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  铃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今为止  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,许许多多  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后我会向前看  变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以许许多多的喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起欢笑  尽情欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无可替代的伙伴们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有过烦恼  有过伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有迷失自我的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们无论何时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论欢喜悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相互扶持  相互交流
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:10:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共同跨越过去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有过争执  有过冲突
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也会相互宽容  相互认同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路欢笑向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要一起走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介你放心  大家都没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都已经搬到安全的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到  你居然能做到这地步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没料到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们比我想象的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要坚强的多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的骄傲  理树
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你终于  超越了我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是恭介的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是追着恭介的背影前进
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是恭介教会了我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活着就会有快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树  快点  起火了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.68,0:13:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫猫猫猫来唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天呀多云转雨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫猫猫猫来唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天是个好天气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:03.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屋檐下面黑幽幽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圈圈下面好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草地上呀冷冰冰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳下面睡觉觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛弯成月牙儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡须就是那勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫猫猫猫来唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.66,0:14:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.62,0:14:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就放学了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.08,0:14:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明拜托真人叫醒我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.13,0:14:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经完全入秋了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:15:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃  理树君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:02.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.85,0:15:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个很Wonderful的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:16.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说宫泽同学回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然抢我的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咔嚓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离那起事故已经过去了三个月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们终于再次重返平凡的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住院的伙伴们也陆续出院
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谦吾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.48,0:15:45.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来的说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.11,0:15:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早点把石膏取下来  我还要跟你一决胜负呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.03,0:15:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一决胜负吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还要斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时老实一段时间吧  少年们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.79,0:16:11.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩恭介同学了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:25.81,up,NTP,0,0,0,,腿部的肌肉就靠这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.31,0:16:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了那么严重的事故  没出人命就已经是奇迹了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:32.69,up,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我们一起买的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.28,0:16:34.19,up,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有不少学生住进了医院
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.49,0:16:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但等到暑假过后的新学期
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大部分人都回到了教室
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.92,0:16:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可最后还有一人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:17:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介依旧昏迷不醒  一直在重症监护室度日
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.59,0:17:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不允许与他人会面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了九月  他被转移到一所规模更大的医院
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.82,0:17:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说不担心  那是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  代替恭介领导Little Busters是我的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们迫不及待地盼望着恭介能够回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  今天做点什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.75,0:18:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一直在等待着  不在此处的最后一人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.97,0:18:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就来踢罐子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.64,0:18:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个玩过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.01,0:18:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在学校里过夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是大白天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.89,0:18:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就试胆大会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.77,0:18:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都秋天了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么人偶剧如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.65,0:18:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个等恭介氏回来后再玩会更热闹些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.61,0:18:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是想不出什么好玩的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然能想到新玩法的只有那家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一人不在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.42,0:19:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那个人的存在却极为重要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快了  他肯定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.39,0:19:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都到齐了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我是在绝佳的时机回来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.90,0:19:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.99,0:19:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很危险的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.03,0:19:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是老样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.16,0:19:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总是这样来吓我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后给我们布置乱七八糟的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就如你所愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.09,0:19:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任务吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新游戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.80,0:19:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来做最有趣的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就我们这些人再去一次修学旅行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.15,0:20:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.68,0:20:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一二  一二  一二…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.10,0:20:35.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我踹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咔嚓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.48,0:20:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  你们准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.28,0:20:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那么就
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.74,0:20:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发咯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.37,0:23:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一次从这里开始
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.50,0:23:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我们「Little Busters」的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会继续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.47,0:23:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到遥远的彼岸
